; Regression test for issue #1692: Output breaks accounting equation
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1692
; When a commodity amount is < 0.5 in default precision, it rounds to 0
; and disappears from balance output, breaking double-entry accounting.

2018-01-01 * Foo
    Assets:A                    2 X @ 0.2 Y
    Assets:B

test bal
                 2 X  Assets:A
end test
